==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Spirifer
<hw>Spi"ri*fer</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[NL., fr. L.
<ets>spira</ets> a coil + <ets>ferre</ets>to bear.]</ety>
<fld>(Paleon.)</fld> <def>Any one of numerous species of fossil
brachipods of the genus <gen>Spirifer</gen>, or <gen>Delthyris</gen>,
and allied genera, in which the long calcareous supports of the arms
form a large spiral, or helix, on each side.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Spirillum</ent>⟦br⟧
